- board should be sized 10x10
- board should contain rows 1..10 and columns A..J
- squares on board should be accessible as "A9" or something similar
- board should be able to contain zero or more ships
- ships may not overlap (but may be adjacent)
- board should indicate whether or not a ship is at a certain square (hit/miss)
- board should allow squares to be updated (hit/miss)
